quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,22,"Ini: \"naâret wid i tepkabarem, war Öebbi. Ur sâin taéeyt ubelkim, deg igenwan ne$ di tmurt; ur criken degsen; ur aS illi, garasen, umâiwen"
  34,23,"Cafuâa, s$uôeS, tenfaâ kan win iwumi ip Irad. Alamma, ma tekkes tugdi seg wulawen nnsen, a d inin: \"acu id Inna, Mass nnwen\"? A d inin: \"d tidep, u Neppa d Aâlayen, d Ameqwôan"
  34,24,"Ini: \"anwa ikwen ip$aten, si tmurt akked igenwan\"? Ini: \"d Öebbi\". Nekwni am kunwi, amendeô ma nella di nnhaya, ne$ di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  34,25,"Ini: \"ur teppuqeîîim $ef wayen nfalîa, ur neppuqeîîi $ef wayen txeddmem"
  34,26,"Ini: \"ad a$ Issemlil Mass nne$, sinna, ad Iêudd garane$, s tidep. Neppa d Amêaddi Amusnaw"
  34,27,"Ini: \"sseknet iyi d wid i tqeônem $uôeS, d icriken\"! Xaîi, Neppa d Öebbi Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"
  34,28,"Ur k id Nuzen, i imdanen, armi d uqniâ; a pbecôôev, a pnedôev. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen, ur ssinen"
  34,29,"Qqaôen: \"melmi lemâahda agi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  34,30,"Ini: \"$uôwen ppaâud ass, ur tezmirem a t teswexxôem, ne$ a t id tesqeôbem, s saâa"